### Data provider tools (read-only; exact names)
- **`data_bars_relative`**: `input` must include **`symbol`**, **`ref_time`** (YYYY-MM-DD), **`count`** (integer; negative = look back in trading days, positive = look forward). Optional **`interval`** (default `"1d"`, e.g. `"1m"`). Optional **`indicators`**: array of [stockstats](https://github.com/jealous/stockstats) column keys. Use for historical OHLCV and indicators — trading-day windows skip weekends and holidays. If `ref_time` is not a trading day, it is silently adjusted to the nearest prior trading day. Symbol must be in the allowlist.
